%F A006522 a(n) = 5*a(n-1) - 10*a(n-2) + 10*a(n-3) - 5*a(n-4) + a(n-5); a(0)=1, a(1)=0, a(2)=0, a(3)=1, a(4)=4. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Jul 11 2011
